    <title>博客主题配置</title>
    <url>/2023/04/25/next-config/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>博客的基本设置和主题相关设置，主题采用next主题。文章中网站根目录都用&lt;hexo&gt;代替。</p>
<span id="more"></span>



<h3 id="1-网站基础设置"><a href="#1-网站基础设置" class="headerlink" title="1. 网站基础设置"></a>1. 网站基础设置</h3><p>打开博客主目录的_config.yml文件，编辑网站名称、描述等</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Site</span><br><span class="line">title: lixp的博客  #网站标题</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: 每天进步一点点  #网站副标题</span><br><span class="line">description: 昨日已逝，明日未至，唯有今日为礼 #网站描述</span><br><span class="line">keywords: </span><br><span class="line">author: lixp  #作者，文章底部显示&quot;本文作者&quot;时，显示该名称</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN #语言，这里配置的是中文</span><br><span class="line">timezone: Asia/Shanghai #时区</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>设置网站访问连接:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: https://lixpbg.github.io #使用搭建好的博客访问地址，这里使用的是github部署的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="2-安装next主题"><a href="#2-安装next主题" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装next主题"></a>2. 安装next主题</h3><p>cd到网站根目录下，安装next主题</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>设置当前主题为next，打开&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;_config.yml配置文件，配置如下:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Extensions</span><br><span class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span><br><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>可以验证主题是否安装成功:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd  &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="3-配置next主题样式"><a href="#3-配置next主题样式" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置next主题样式"></a>3. 配置next主题样式</h3><p><strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml 文件，有四种不同的样式，可以自己选择，这里选择了最新的Gemini样式</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>点下面链接浏览不同的样式:</p>
<p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/muse/">Muse</a> | <a href="https://theme-next.js.org/mist/">Mist</a> | <a href="https://theme-next.js.org/pisces/">Pisces</a> | <a href="https://theme-next.js.org/">Gemini</a></p>
<h3 id="4-配置菜单栏"><a href="#4-配置菜单栏" class="headerlink" title="4. 配置菜单栏"></a>4. 配置菜单栏</h3><h4 id="4-1-菜单栏基础配置"><a href="#4-1-菜单栏基础配置" class="headerlink" title="4.1 菜单栏基础配置"></a>4.1 菜单栏基础配置</h4><p><strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml，找到menu配置，目前只配置首页,关于，标签，分类，归档。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home  #首页</span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/ || fa fa-user #关于页面</span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || fa fa-tags  #标签</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || fa fa-th #分类</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive #归档</span><br><span class="line">  #schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span><br><span class="line">  #sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  #commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="4-2-生成标签页面"><a href="#4-2-生成标签页面" class="headerlink" title="4.2 生成标签页面"></a>4.2 生成标签页面</h4><p>执行如下命令，生成标签页面</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>打开生成的模板文件 <code>&lt;hexo&gt;/source/tags/index.md</code></p>
<p>修改模板内容，主要是<strong>type: tags</strong>:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-04-26 13:53:05</span><br><span class="line">type: tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>在文章中使用标签，两种方式选1种就可以:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 这是文章的标题</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#第一种方式,多个标签用中括号括起来</span><br><span class="line">tags: [标签1, 标签2]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#第二种方式,单独列出来</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">	- 标签1</span><br><span class="line">	- 标签2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="4-3-生成分类页面"><a href="#4-3-生成分类页面" class="headerlink" title="4.3 生成分类页面"></a>4.3 生成分类页面</h4><p>在终端执行命令,生成分类页面</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑分类模板 <code>&lt;hexo&gt;/source/categories/index.md</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-04-26 13:59:26</span><br><span class="line">type: categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>在文章中指定分类:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 这是文章的标题</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#文章涉及到的标签</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">	- 标签1</span><br><span class="line">	- 标签2</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">#文章的分类，这里需要注意，hexo规定文章一般只属于一个分类，所有此处 分类2 是 分类1的子分类，不是同级的</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">	- 分类1</span><br><span class="line">	- 分类2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="4-4-生成归档页面"><a href="#4-4-生成归档页面" class="headerlink" title="4.4 生成归档页面"></a>4.4 生成归档页面</h4><p>终端执行执行指令:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page archives</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>编辑归档 <code>&lt;hexo&gt;/source/archives/index.md</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 归档</span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-04-26 14:23:07</span><br><span class="line">type: archives</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="4-5-生关于页面"><a href="#4-5-生关于页面" class="headerlink" title="4.5 生关于页面"></a>4.5 生关于页面</h4><p>终端执行指令:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="4-6-404页面"><a href="#4-6-404页面" class="headerlink" title="4.6 404页面"></a>4.6 404页面</h4><p>当某个页面找不到时，显示自定义的404页面</p>
<p>终端执行指令:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="5-配置头像"><a href="#5-配置头像" class="headerlink" title="5. 配置头像"></a>5. 配置头像</h3><p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml,找到avatar配置项:</p>
<p>找一张图片，将图片拷贝到<code>&lt;hexo&gt;/node_modules/hexo-theme-next/source/images</code>目录下，然后在配置，在主题配置文件中设置url字段，我的图片名为avatar1.jpeg</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Sidebar Avatar</span><br><span class="line">avatar:</span><br><span class="line">  # Replace the default image and set the url here.</span><br><span class="line">  url: /images/avatar1.jpeg #/images/avatar.gif</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar will be displayed in circle.</span><br><span class="line">  rounded: false</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.</span><br><span class="line">  rotated: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="6-配置本地搜索"><a href="#6-配置本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="6. 配置本地搜索"></a>6. 配置本地搜索</h3><p>安装本地搜索插件，执行指令:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>编辑<strong>网站配置文件</strong>(<code>&lt;hexo&gt;/_config.yml</code>),在文件中添加如下配置:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  content: true</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml,将enable设置为true:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Local Search</span><br><span class="line"># Dependencies: https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # If auto, trigger search by changing input.</span><br><span class="line">  # If manual, trigger search by pressing enter key or search button.</span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br><span class="line">  # Show top n results per article, show all results by setting to -1</span><br><span class="line">  top_n_per_article: 1</span><br><span class="line">  # Unescape html strings to the readable one.</span><br><span class="line">  unescape: false</span><br><span class="line">  # Preload the search data when the page loads.</span><br><span class="line">  preload: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="7-添加浏览量"><a href="#7-添加浏览量" class="headerlink" title="7. 添加浏览量"></a>7. 添加浏览量</h3><p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml,将enable设置为true:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors_icon: fa fa-user</span><br><span class="line">  total_views: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_views_icon: fa fa-eye</span><br><span class="line">  post_views: true</span><br><span class="line">  post_views_icon: far fa-eye</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="8-添加社交链接"><a href="#8-添加社交链接" class="headerlink" title="8. 添加社交链接"></a>8. 添加社交链接</h3><p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml，选择部分链接配置。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">  GitHub: https://github.com || fab fa-github</span><br><span class="line">  E-Mail: mailto:yourname@gmail.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br><span class="line">  #Weibo: https://weibo.com/yourname || fab fa-weibo</span><br><span class="line">  #Twitter: https://twitter.com/yourname || fab fa-twitter</span><br><span class="line">  #FB Page: https://www.facebook.com/yourname || fab fa-facebook</span><br><span class="line">  #StackOverflow: https://stackoverflow.com/yourname || fab fa-stack-overflow</span><br><span class="line">  #YouTube: https://youtube.com/yourname || fab fa-youtube</span><br><span class="line">  #Instagram: https://instagram.com/yourname || fab fa-instagram</span><br><span class="line">  #Skype: skype:yourname?call|chat || fab fa-skype</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="9-配置阅读进度"><a href="#9-配置阅读进度" class="headerlink" title="9. 配置阅读进度"></a>9. 配置阅读进度</h3><p>在看博客时，页面顶部会出现一个阅读进度条。</p>
<p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml,将reading_progress —&gt; enable改为true.</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Reading progress bar</span><br><span class="line">reading_progress:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: left | right</span><br><span class="line">  start_at: left</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: top | bottom</span><br><span class="line">  position: top</span><br><span class="line">  reversed: false</span><br><span class="line">  color: &quot;#37c6c0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  height: 3px</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="10-设置文章底部的版权信息"><a href="#10-设置文章底部的版权信息" class="headerlink" title="10. 设置文章底部的版权信息"></a>10. 设置文章底部的版权信息</h3><p>编辑<strong>主题配置文件</strong>&lt;hexo&gt;&#x2F;node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml,将其中的sidebar 和 post 设置为true</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">creative_commons:</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: by | by-nc | by-nc-nd | by-nc-sa | by-nd | by-sa | cc-zero</span><br><span class="line">  license: by-nc-sa</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: big | small</span><br><span class="line">  size: small</span><br><span class="line">  sidebar: true</span><br><span class="line">  post: true</span><br><span class="line">  # You can set a language value if you prefer a translated version of CC license, e.g. deed.zh</span><br><span class="line">  # CC licenses are available in 39 languages, you can find the specific and correct abbreviation you need on https://creativecommons.org</span><br><span class="line">  language:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="11-显示阅读更多"><a href="#11-显示阅读更多" class="headerlink" title="11. 显示阅读更多"></a>11. 显示阅读更多</h3><p>在文章添加如下标签:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="12-配置博客图片以相对路径显示"><a href="#12-配置博客图片以相对路径显示" class="headerlink" title="12. 配置博客图片以相对路径显示"></a>12. 配置博客图片以相对路径显示</h3><p><strong>如果图片是存储在如七牛云等云平台时，则不用此方法</strong></p>
<p>安装插件，可以在文章中以markdown的方式访问图片</p>
<p>执行命令:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;hexo&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-marked</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>编辑博客主目录的_config.yml文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_asset_folder: true</span><br><span class="line">marked:</span><br><span class="line">  prependRoot: true</span><br><span class="line">  postAsset: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>配置好之后，每次在hexo new page “xxx”的时候，都会生成一个跟文章文件名相同的目录，将改文章的图片放入该目录即可，在写文章时可以用markdown语法引用图片:</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](xxx.png) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注意: 这种引用方式typora中图片显示不出来，只有部署之后才能在网站显示</p>
